caption.p: Differential expression of ACE2 and TMPRSS2. The RNA sequencing data was obtained from the NCBI database (Bioproject, PRJEB4337) submitted by a previous study [ 96]. The raw reads were aligned to the human genome, and differential gene expression was determined using Partek Flow Software.
